cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision techniques (DeepDream) applied to videos, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.MM) and proposes modifications to improve control and aesthetic appeal (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of loss functions to improve the output (cs.AI) and discusses the mitigation of artifacts (cs.GR).
